STATE
v.
Jennifer JIMENEZ/April Myers 22P19-3 Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 14, 2019 April Myers, For Jimenez, Jennifer James R. O'Neill, District Attorney, For the State of North Carolina.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 25th of June 2019 by Defendant to Recall Order for Arrest; Failure to Appear; Strike Called and Failed; and to Set Aside Bond Forfeiture:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 14th of August 2019."
